thread.title: CathyO'Riley

author: CathyO'Riley
title: CathyO'Riley
text: Steven, Ryan and the staff at Nelson Alexander were so professional and helpful to deal with. As someone who was not familiar with the auction process, they advised every step of the way and ensured it all went to plan. I was always given plenty of notice for inspections and this saved an enormous amount of stress. They achieved a fantastic result for me on the day and i would have no hesitation in recommending them to anyone. Thanks again to Steven, Ryan and all the staff at Nelson Alexander.
